{"tid":2139752,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"39歲卡斯拿斯宣佈退役","createTime":"2020-08-04T13:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T04:20:25.000Z","uid":16659,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"5c24e7b4a070cb7e439fc0edb8354aa55cbb85b7","tid":2139752,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:13:55.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】39歲傳奇門將卡斯拿斯已沒有比賽多時，周二終於宣佈退役。<br />\n<br />\n卡斯拿斯（Iker Casillas）在Twitter發出聲明：「最重要是你走過的路及陪伴你的人，不是這些引領你去到的地方。我想我可以毫不猶豫地說，這是一個夢想般的旅程和目的地。」<br />\n<br />\n聖卡斯在9歲便加入皇家馬德里，上陣了725場，贏過5次西甲、3次歐聯等19個冠軍。雖然於2015年盛傳被逼離隊，但他最近已經回歸母會擔任顧問。卡斯拿斯在聲明中也特別提到：「我屬於皇馬，永遠都是。」<br />\n<br />\n卡斯拿斯歷來為西班牙國家隊出戰167場，是狂牛於2008至12年連贏2次歐國盃、1次世界盃的功臣。他在2015年改投波圖，贏過2次葡超，但於去年5月操練時心臟病發，完成手術後一直未有再度披甲。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : Twitter圖片"},{"pid":"fb4937cf4dfdbfa3497bd6ce656bbe2aae3a822e","tid":2139752,"uid":12628,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:57:30.000Z","msg":"保方仲打緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240be9ae23c59f8f8f8aeb930cc91d529ee4a48b","tid":2139752,"uid":199292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:58:20.000Z","msg":"佩狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fcebe9c6035f2aa28fabfab66aa6f706c821f29","tid":2139752,"uid":86980,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fb4937cf4dfdbfa3497bd6ce656bbe2aae3a822e","tid":2139752,"uid":12628,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:57:30.000Z","msg":"保方仲打緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:59:51.000Z","msg":"保住後方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9de9ba85c6f6d122b5a710044387d57e74be927f","tid":2139752,"uid":16659,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T14:20:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.